<div class="pictures4mobile">
<div class="scp-image-block block-center" style="width:300;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/the-author-page-of-a-cute-fish/fish.png" style="width:300;" alt="fish.png" class="image" />
